QuestData.Title: Rush Delivery
QuestData.Description: Peak Grindstone's team broke down somewhere out there to the west.$B$BThink you can make yourself useful for a change and rush some parts out to them, $r?
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Catapult Parts to Peak Grindstone on the Fractured Front in Deepholm.
QuestData.CompletionText: Are those spare parts you have there?
QuestData.RewardText: I can't thank you enough, $c. Now, let's see if we can get this catapult moving again.
